oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Clinical efficacy of chlortetracycline hydrochloride administered in milk replacer to calves
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Braidwood, J. C.
Henry, N. W.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: immunological status
zinc sulphate
turbidity values
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Two similar groups of 14 calves were housed and fed identically in individual pens on a calf-rearing farm. The groups were balanced for weight and immunological status as determined by zinc sulphate turbidity values. Full article published in Veterinary Record (1990) 127, 197-301
